DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$x0 = random(-2,2,1);
$y0 = non_zero_random(-2,2,1);
$a = random(2,6,1);
$c = random(2,4,1);
$b = $a*$x0**2 - $c*$y0**2;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

For the equation given below, evaluate \(y'\) at the point
\(($x0,$y0)\).
\[
    $c y^2 - $a x^2 ? {$b} = 0.
\]
$BR
$BR
\(y'\) at \(($x0,$y0)\) = \{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans = $a*$x0/($c*$y0);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();
